Getting Private key
[nancy001@griffon-49 tmp]$ openssl x509 -req -in demande-user-sigca.csr -out certif-user-sigca.crt -CA certif-CA.crt -CAkey cle-CA.key -CAcreateserial -CAserial CA.srl
Signature ok
subject=/C=FR/O=GRID5000/OU=STAFF/CN=Sebastien BADIA 1407
Getting CA Private Key
[nancy001@griffon-49 tmp]$

cp certif-user-sigca.crt usercert.pem
